@layout MarkdownLayout
@page "/blog/second"
@{
    Page.Title = "Second post";
    Page.InFeed = true; //Requires a @page directive to be discovered
    Page.Published = "2025-07-02";
}

Without inheriting the type @(nameof(BlogPost)) a razor page need:

- A @@page directive - to be found.
- `InFeed = true`

This post was written in markdown using `@@layout MarkdownLayout`.

